<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Забыл пароль</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logo2.png">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .form-container {
            max-width: 400px;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 32px 24px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #212121;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 100px auto;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .logo-container {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #1778f2;
        }

        h4 {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: normal;
            color: #555;
        }

        .form-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .form-group label {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .form-group input {
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }

        .form-group input::placeholder {
            color: #999;
        }

        .form-group input:focus {
            border-color: #1778f2;
            outline: none;
        }

        .form-submit-btn {
            background-color: #1778f2;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .form-submit-btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .signup-link {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .signup-link a {
            color: #1778f2;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .signup-link a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="form-container" id="emailForm">
    <div class="logo-container">
        Забыл пароль
    </div>
    <h4>Мы отправим код подтверждения аккаунта на вашу почту.</h4>

    <form class="form" action="/auth/send-email" method="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Эл. адрес</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Введите свой эл. адрес" required>
        </div>
        <br>
        <button class="form-submit-btn" type="submit">Отправить код</button>
    </form>

    <p class="signup-link">
        У вас нет аккаунта?
        <a href="/auth/register" class="signup-link link"> Создать</a>
    </p>
</div>
<script src="/javascripts/warning.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
